reviewText: Sent as a gift, haven't seen it.

I already knew about this family and their seven high human pyramid on the highwire but this is an excellent DVD. The other DVD which shows them is "Circus Flora" and you get to know the family and the relativies who compose the act. You do see how committed this family is to keeping the true original circus alive with this spell binding act.
I love this DVD and often play it while I'm on my elliptical trainer. What a great, loving and dedicated family!
